reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: Excellent sound quality for the price
reviews.reviewText: These Tuneflux headphones are built solidly. Nothing creaks, rattles or feels cheap. They look and feel like a much higher price product. The thing that surprised me the most however, was the sound. Clear and accentuated trebles, mids maybe a little flat but still natural, and bass - rich, deep and controlled. I put some of my reference rock songs through them and Tuneflux came out with no shame at all. They sound very comparable to Anker Soundcore Life Q20 ( twice the price), better than 1More Sonoflow ( more than twice the price ).
